{"tid":714243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係巴士到同小朋友玩既家長究竟係咩心態？","createTime":"2018-06-23T14:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T09:16:31.000Z","uid":171277,"like":15,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7230818bd49b3743776747af93e50c1b524401eb","tid":714243,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩收工搭巴士，就遇著個家庭，小朋友幾得意好精靈，父母看似都係善男信女，如果冇估錯，應該係一個幸福美滿既家庭<br />\n<br />\n佢地好開心咁同小朋友玩，，一個羨煞旁人既美麗畫面亦隨即影入眼簾<br />\n<br />\n不過，美麗的背後，往往要付出代價<br />\n<br />\n係巴士咁細既空間入面，小朋友既一顰一笑對其他乘客而言都只係騷擾<br />\n<br />\n當時我坐正中間<br />\n<br />\n坐我左手邊既係一個玩得好開心既幸福家庭，<br />\n坐我右手邊就係一堆dup低頭，合埋眼，但同時亦縐實眉頭既乘客<br />\n<br />\n若要形容眼前既畫面，一念天堂一念地獄之外，就最適合不過<br />\n<br />\n小朋友細個唔識野，開心就會又尖叫又大笑，我唔怪佢<br />\n<br />\n但家長冇即時叫佢安靜d，反而仲同佢玩等佢keep住嘈究竟係咩心態？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6044a4c381431991f56bb1890f5d8ec6fb157cc1","tid":714243,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869119208fb1b5a2a58b55ebc593ddf3fb8cf209","tid":714243,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d929f04c3f9de4ef7b94aeb0193664a4757ace5a","tid":714243,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee5f0d69d654172059e7215e835e2758e95310e","tid":714243,"uid":171277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf53db51fb1830dd1b1be32c26c87e0856118b7","tid":714243,"uid":150982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"因為家長唔想自己小朋友得米五"},{"pid":"c72ec3245491b4cdca4bae2a187e920c12dfa23e","tid":714243